{"tid":492810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[累己累人]女生確診肺癆惟未按指示治療　衛生署將發隔離令","createTime":"2017-12-08T01:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T10:06:38.000Z","uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5efb76ca333246db40a4bb5c624dd65f65d2d010","tid":492810,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:58:13.000Z","msg":"消息透露，一名12歲的中一女生在確診抗藥性肺癆後，未有按醫生指示完成治療，衞生署將發出隔離令，強制女生到那打素醫院隔離治療，並會要求警方協助。社署亦會跟進有關學生的家庭需要。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署回覆查詢時說不評論個別個案，只表示正跟進沙田一所中學的結核病個案。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署說，由於結核病由感染到發病可能會醞釀一段時間，預期未來數月仍可能出現少數個案。署方胸肺科已安排校內與患者接觸比較緊密的師生，接受篩查及預防治療。<br />\n<br />\n署方又指，根據《預防及控制疾病規例》第23條，如衞生主任有理由相信某人感染特定傳染病，可藉書面命令隔離感染者。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1368985-20171208.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1368985-20171208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WhVtFhm6MzdxFGSq8%2FK8QRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ef30a053\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1368985-20171208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6719a652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1368985-20171208.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"abd6f56b5117d7f6db59fb994be15dd6648e1c4f","tid":492810,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7cef3594783c76535b8eef27be180c165189f1","tid":492810,"uid":28031,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:03:26.000Z","msg":"人道毀滅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0986a2c1ad32f2831b6c7f28116179c01318a9","tid":492810,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:03:32.000Z","msg":"起佢底"},{"pid":"e4fc3f8d978344829cf8f00d4849ce0d60a59c57","tid":492810,"uid":22218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:05:28.000Z","msg":"因為要考呈分試？"},{"pid":"89caea7c1172a3f8112ca75c711223ecea0d1e68","tid":492810,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:06:16.000Z","msg":"隔離醫好之後應該要捉去坐監 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf64be1fe0d0f34236d1d7401573e2f42d1f5de","tid":492810,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:09:33.000Z","msg":"仆街"},{"pid":"3c26a3f6cb7ca5346c396b47d4820bf024e97fa0","tid":492810,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:10:35.000Z","msg":"會唔會係雙非"},{"pid":"c6665ef6946df33c4bafc65ce1c3d85503e55c39","tid":492810,"uid":130105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:12:04.000Z","msg":"九成冇咳就唔食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4d1bc6a465c697e2d0d2ef2335c29d3537ca74","tid":492810,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:14:23.000Z","msg":"希望拉佢去打靶"},{"pid":"09b378306da3c942fb0b57e66eb2f4fce7c3406a","tid":492810,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"買樓希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c6fe177af8305f8a7afd6f16b24b32e9bd0123","tid":492810,"uid":154385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:19:25.000Z","msg":"又係哥類仆街老豆老母 自然療法"},{"pid":"7dc6ad649db8e75c2cb12d2bb9bcbb43a1c55